  FROM dba_hist_sqlstat s,
       dba_hist_snapshot sn
 WHERE s.snap_id = sn.snap_id

   AND s.snap_id BETWEEN 1941 AND 4863
 ORDER BY s.snap_id desc, s.instance_number, s.plan_hash_value;
